<subSubSection pageId="20" pageNumber="21" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="20.[151,1437,933,1930]" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,284,933,959]" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">Etymology</emphasis>
. We are pleased to name this genus in memory of the late Frank T. Hovore for his friendship and many contributions to the study of 
<taxonomicName box="[561,734,970,996]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="20" pageNumber="21" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Cerambycidae</taxonomicName>
. Masculine gender.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
